information: The company WOLF LAND-, FÖRDER- UND GARTENTECHNIK, MIETPARK U. REPARATUR-WERKSTATT INHABER THOMAS WOLF E.K., is a Distributor, founded in 1935, which operates in the Indoor and greenhouse plants, floristry industry. It also operates in the Hardware, building construction, Industrial hardware, Agricultural systems and equipment, and Agriculture and forestry - machinery and equipment industries. It is based in Bad Neustadt, Germany.
